Disclaimer / Security Notice:
This joomla extension stores your password in your site's database, it does not share your contact info nor your credentials with anyone. This extension does not collect your username or password, it just allows you to stotre it in YOUR site's database in order to fulfill its purpose, which is to retrieve your reading list's items.
JGReader and its author(s) are not responsible for any data loss that may occur by the user of this extension.
